direction: down

req: Request id method params { icon: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/heroicons@2.1.1/24/outline/arrow-right-circle.svg }
res: Response id result or error { icon: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/heroicons@2.1.1/24/outline/arrow-uturn-left.svg }
notif: Notification method params no id { icon: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/heroicons@2.1.1/24/outline/bell.svg }

req -> res: pairs with
req -> notif: contrasts with
